articles.title: Vulcan Centaur Set to Launch Tomorrow, but Will It Become America’s Next Big Rocket? - Gizmodo
articles.description: ULA's heavy-lift rocket is poised to make a big impact in the industry, but tomorrow's second launch will need to go well for that to happen.
